A middle-aged man in colorful tight cycling gear rides a road bike through a moonlit Singapore cemetery at night, surrounded by traditional Chinese tombstones and tropical vegetation. The scene is rendered in Studio Ghibli animation style with soft, ethereal lighting from paper lanterns and fireflies dotting the darkness. Wispy mist curls between ornate grave markers while tropical frangipani trees frame the path. The cyclist appears joyful and determined, his figure slightly exaggerated in the whimsical Ghibli fashion. The night sky shows a brilliant full moon casting silver light across the scene, with distant Singapore high-rises glowing on the horizon. The atmosphere balances the mysterious cemetery setting with warmth and adventure rather than fear.
